text: Hato Corozal Airport is an airport serving the town of Hato Corozal, in the Casanare Department of Colombia. The runway is on the southeast side of the town, and has an additional of grass overrun on the southwest end. ==See also== * * *Transport in Colombia *List of airports in Colombia ==References== ==External links== *OpenStreetMap - Hato Corozal *OurAirports - Hato Corozal *FallingRain - Hato Corozal Category:Airports in Colombia Category:Colombia transport-related lists
